        <font color="white" face="Verdana" size="2"> Just thought I’d blow off a little virtual steam.. hope you guys don’t mind my venting here ;)</P><P>I’m a level 60 Necromancer.. powerful dude, killer of Wizzies and Master of Jobobber…</P><P>I paid my Dues and can say that I’m pretty proud of my accomplishments.</P><P>I play on a Blue server. I sometimes wish I had started on a red server. (This mostly comes up when some joker is giving me grief or hassling one of my lower level alts.)</P><P>I made a Necro on Sullon Zek… I looked at the numbers, the zones that were controlled by the Evils over the Goods. The sheer staggering number of Evil players versus Good players. There wasn’t much challenge to that. (I also read the Fansy the Famous Bard threads and thought that was some funny stuff.)</P><P>So I deleted my Iksar Necro on SZ and made a Human Wizard (Good guy.)</P><P>I made level 5 and headed to Odus (Small scrap of land that was “Owned” by the good team.)</P><P>Entered Paineel newbie zone and some high level Necro comes and looks at me. (He’s level 34) He tries to cast something on me, but at level 5 he couldn’t get it to land. (I see the swirling green myst of the root spell attempting to form around me.) He tries two or three more times, smiles at me and walks off.</P><P>I make level 6 and enter The Warens. Some level 51 Shadowknight is hanging out RIGHT at the zone in and runs at me. His first swing misses, his next swing hits for 50-something. I backed up and zoned out. Then I ran and hid near the entrance to The Hole.</P><P>I saw this guy zoning in and out of Warens, running all over looking for me. I couldn’t enjoy my time at all for about 20 minutes while this went on. (I zoned into Warens once more about 10 mins later and saw him running at me and backed out.)</P><P>Now.. I’m all for brawling and defending yourself. Dog eat Dog etc… but a level 34 Necro and a level 51 SK hunting a level 5/6 Wizard for over a half hour like I was some hot chick in an all male prison was a little absurd. I mean..</P><P>First, Verant should make the PVP limit 10 or 20 levels at least. </P><P>Second, get a life you weenie butt spank pussy nerd. You wanna brawl come to Bristlebane and /d me… punk-ass wannabe Necro and Loser Shadownot… chasing and killing baby characters is about as lame as it gets. Go club a baby seal...</P><P>Ahhh… I feel much better now :)</P><P>P.S.<BR>This wasn’t directed at Necros or SK’s in General (I love you guys man.), just people that get their jollies killing someone 30, 40 or 50 levels lower than them. ;)</P><P><BR><img src="http://www.jackntracie.com/images/gojirax.jpg" border=0></P><P>Edited by - Gojirax on 08/28/2002  15:02:54</P><P>Edited by - Gojirax on 08/28/2002  15:03:17</font></td>

